      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Skill: InlineExtract\n\n**Category:** Structural / Transformational Skill\n\n**Intent:** Move structure between abstraction layers to optimize clarity or reuse.\n\nInlineExtract changes *where structure lives*, not *what it means*.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
