      "width": 760,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Scope\n\n### This skill:\n- Inlines referenced structures\n- Extracts repeated structures\n- Updates references explicitly\n- Preserves semantic relationships\n\n### This skill does NOT:\n- Change meaning\n- Reorder unless explicit\n- Touch unrelated structure",
